                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9387" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1064</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1053 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">慧眼识“机”：雪利曼的创业转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Seeing the Opportunity: Sherryman&#39;s Road to Entrepreneurial Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">齐培培，徐璨，毕宏波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁波财经学院*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁波市海曙雪利曼电子仪表有限公司 </td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仪器、仪表工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业者；创业机会识别；机会窗口；创业机会评价模型；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Entrepreneurs; Entrepreneurial Opportunity Identification; Window of Opportunity; Entrepreneurial Opportunity Evaluation Models</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了童卫明和童林辉父子将一个小机械仪表厂一步步发展成为集汽车仪表研发、生产、销售为一体的专业化生产企业、技术平台车联网先进企业的创业历程。引导学生围绕雪利曼的两次创业转型，思考创业者如何识别机会、抓住机遇进而推动公司创业成长的过程，深化学生对于创业机会识别过程模型与机会评价模型的理解，认识到创业机会是创业者与环境的互动过程中逐步形成的，好的创业机会需要与团队、资源和环境相匹配，了解创业机会识别的影响因素以及机会窗口的概念。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the entrepreneurial journey of Tong Weiming and Tong Linhui, a father and son, who have developed a small mechanical instrumentation factory step by step into a specialized production enterprise integrating the research and development, production and sales of automotive instrumentation, and an advanced enterprise of technological platform car networking. Students are guided to focus on Sherryman&#39;s two entrepreneurial transformation, think about how entrepreneurs identify opportunities, seize opportunities and then promote the process of entrepreneurial growth of the company, deepen students&#39; understanding of the entrepreneurial opportunity identification process model and the opportunity evaluation model, realize that entrepreneurial opportunities are gradually formed in the process of entrepreneurial interaction with the environment, and that good entrepreneurial opportunities need to be matched with the team, resources and the environment, and learn about the entrepreneurial opportunity identification influencing factors and the concept of window of opportunity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业者与环境互动的机会识别过程模型；创业机会识别：机会识别的影响因素、机会发现的二维框架；创业机会的分类；机会窗口的概念；创业机会评价模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
